{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"19a45925d5","title":"中专教师的右派言论（二）","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（四）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编印，1957年11月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"533950ac23","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"19a45925d5"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0fa7d3988d","name":"山西"},{"id":"27bb353a49","name":"陈明谟"},{"id":"a7c6b9df01","name":"田子清"},{"id":"ae38fbf6b2","name":"兰文华"},{"id":"f72223ca2f","name":"陈鸿钧"},{"id":"f99fae35a4","name":"李觉生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3bae588a1f","type":"title","text":"中专教师的右派言论（二）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"19a45925d5"},{"id":"b22ecb2f54","type":"authors","text":"山西田子清陈鸿钧陈明谟李觉生兰文华","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"19a45925d5"},{"id":"46bf54f130","type":"paragraph","text":"田子清（忻县专区文补校教师）：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"19a45925d5"},{"id":"f8625762d8","type":"paragraph","text":"“共产党过去承认错误很少，拿辩证法来当挡箭牌，只靠党来吃饭没力量，只拿空洞的马列主义是领导不了的”。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"19a45925d5"},{"id":"2aa7982abc","type":"paragraph","text":"陈鸿钧（化工学校教师）：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"19a45925d5"},{"id":"167836cc32","type":"paragraph","text":"“人生就是为了名和利，名利决定一切，是发展的动力，例如黄继光，虽然死了，也是为了名誉。科学家进行科学研究，是为名誉和利益。现在共产党和民盟是为了争权夺利，在现在的社会中对人处事，也需要‘拍’，不过是拍的方式、方法和旧社会不同。大部分党员就是因为会拍才拍上去的。我们学校的党员中，有40—60%是通过拍，而上去的。我不会新的拍的方法，所以上不去”。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"19a45925d5"},{"id":"58b9255eea","type":"paragraph","text":"陈明谟（机械工业学校教师）：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"19a45925d5"},{"id":"2738c6477e","type":"paragraph","text":"“知识分子的特点是‘士为知己者用，士可杀不可辱’，应以刘备三顾茅庐的精神来信任知识分子”。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"19a45925d5"},{"id":"e417a8210d","type":"paragraph","text":"李觉生（长治师范教师）：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"19a45925d5"},{"id":"4a27fa0970","type":"paragraph","text":"“百花齐放、百家争鸣是诱敌深入，聚而歼之，叫人上当”。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"19a45925d5"},{"id":"cc0a9a8d13","type":"paragraph","text":"兰文华（太谷师范教师）：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"19a45925d5"},{"id":"a3aab5495b","type":"paragraph","text":"“统购统销不够吃，想吃的东西买不到。高级干部要啥有啥，北京给高级干部设有副食杂货公司，如果说这是对毛主席的爱戴关怀，我看过去也可说是对蒋介石的爱戴关怀”。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"19a45925d5"}],"page":{"id":"5674f8d5be","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"19a45925d5","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}